{"title":"BiKASE Sidewinder “Any Bottle Cage” fits Bigger Bottles on Smaller Bikes","link":"https://bikerumor.com/bikase-sidewinder-any-bottle-cage-fits-bigger-bottles-on-smaller-bikes/","date":1690235150000,"content":"<p>BiKASE’s original ABC (Any Bottle Cage) used an expandable cage design with a ratcheting closure to secure the contents, allowing you to fit something larger, like a Nalgene bottle. Or, attach it to your fork legs and stow a small tent, sleeping bag, or dry bag.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/bikase-sidewinder-ABC-expandable-bottle-cage-3.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"988\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/bikase-sidewinder-ABC-expandable-bottle-cage-3.jpg\" alt=\"bikase sidewinder ABC adjustable size bicycle bottle cage shown with nalgene and wine bottle in it\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/bikase-sidewinder-ABC-expandable-bottle-cage-3.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/bikase-sidewinder-ABC-expandable-bottle-cage-3-297x147.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/bikase-sidewinder-ABC-expandable-bottle-cage-3-800x395.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/bikase-sidewinder-ABC-expandable-bottle-cage-3-120x59.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/bikase-sidewinder-ABC-expandable-bottle-cage-3-768x379.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/bikase-sidewinder-ABC-expandable-bottle-cage-3-1536x759.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>Now, their Sidewider ABC tilts things to allow for side entry, making it possible to slip larger bottles (or gear) into frames with less space inside the front triangle. Whether that’s a kids’ bike, or just a really small frame or challenging full suspension layout, now you have more options and a system that’ll hold the contents tight no matter what the terrain.</p>\n\n\n\n<figure><a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/bikase-sidewinder-ABC-expandable-bottle-cage-2.jpg\"><img width=\"2000\" height=\"989\" src=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/bikase-sidewinder-ABC-expandable-bottle-cage-2.jpg\" alt=\"bikase sidewinder ABC adjustable size bicycle bottle cage\" srcset=\"https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/bikase-sidewinder-ABC-expandable-bottle-cage-2.jpg 2000w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/bikase-sidewinder-ABC-expandable-bottle-cage-2-297x147.jpg 297w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/bikase-sidewinder-ABC-expandable-bottle-cage-2-800x396.jpg 800w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/bikase-sidewinder-ABC-expandable-bottle-cage-2-120x59.jpg 120w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/bikase-sidewinder-ABC-expandable-bottle-cage-2-768x380.jpg 768w, https://bikerumor.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/bikase-sidewinder-ABC-expandable-bottle-cage-2-1536x760.jpg 1536w\" /></a></figure>\n\n\n\n<p>The Sidewinder can be flip-flopped for right or left side entry, and the opening goes from 2.25″ up to 4.75″. MSRP is $29.99.</p>\n\n\n\n<p><em><a href=\"https://bikase.com/products/sidewinder-abc-cage\" target=\"_blank\">BiKASE.com</a></em></p>\n<p>The post <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com/bikase-sidewinder-any-bottle-cage-fits-bigger-bottles-on-smaller-bikes/\">BiKASE Sidewinder “Any Bottle Cage” fits Bigger Bottles on Smaller Bikes</a> appeared first on <a href=\"https://bikerumor.com\">Bikerumor</a>.</p>","author":"Tyler Benedict","siteTitle":"Bikerumor","siteHash":"49f427af0a926f4232eb837006841d7242e153e3afbb590f32e4b104ea3e2718","entryHash":"fa333462c50d6ffc5626086da972fccc05c902ceb90f9397671dd7ca638e8d29","category":"Cycling"}